<br>
All of these tests were preformed using Shock Of Steal, Which I am specilized in.<br>
<br>
Through all of these tests I had 196Int (I stripped down a bit to get below 200int)<br>
<br>
The Spell SoSteel, Took 11% of my mana to cast (before savings spells always require the full cost of the spell to cast). This of course ment I had 2500 Mana, I doubled checked this on a mana calk and it indeed did come too 2509 mana. This mana was Constant throughout  all the tests.<br>
<br>
